      <scopecontent id="aspace_755dc683e0505f399f2881a0af73936b">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of reports, subject files, agreements, tax and audit files, financial statements, and memoranda documenting the operations of the assistant comptroller for estates, trusts and taxes at Yale.</p>  
